data.description: This recently renovated 3 bed 2 bath ranch home is an amazing find just 15 minutes from downtown Salisbury. Great for a young family since the home resides in a quiet community and close to all three school levels. If you are looking for a "move-in" ready home that is safe and clean, you have found it. With an ADT security system and a newly encapsulated crawl space with a modern technology dehumidifier, you will definitely feel safe and secure. This home was completely updated in 2018 with such things as a new roof, new windows, new HVAC, gorgeous bamboo flooring, fully updated kitchen and bathrooms, and a well organized laundry room with modern cabinets for extra storage. 1-year home warranty. There is a flex room that can be either a bonus room or an office space with glass french doors for privacy. There is also plenty of room in the front and back yards for kids to play or to create a family vegetable garden. You will need to see to believe this rural diamond of a home.
